This paper deals with the problem of multi-objective recommender systems, which is a subfield of information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also proposes a novel learning-to-re-rank approach, which involves machine learning techniques (cs.LG). The problem of optimizing online marketplaces involves considerations of cybersecurity (cs.CY) and data science (cs.DS). Finally, the paper also deals with the problem of multiple stakeholders, which could be considered a social and information network analysis problem (cs.SI).
